Fetch Delphi's digital surveillance sensors

Source: R/endpoints.R
pvt_sensors.Rd

API docs: https://cmu-delphi.github.io/delphi-epidata/api/sensors.html

pvt_sensors(auth, names, locations, epiweeks)

Arguments

auth

string. Your authentication key.

names

character vector. The names of the sensors to fetch.

locations

character vector. The locations to fetch.

epiweeks

epirange. The epiweeks to fetch.

Value

epidata_call

Examples

# \donttest{
call <- pvt_sensors(auth = "yourkey", names = "sar3", locations = "nat", epiweeks = epirange(201501, 202001))
fetch_classic(call)
